ferrn

The goal of ferrn is to Facilitate the Exploration of touRR optimisatioN, thus ferrn.

Installation

You can install the development version of ferrn from GitHub with:

# install.packages("devtools")
#devtools::install_github("huizezhang-sherry/ferrn")

Example

This is a basic example which shows you how to solve a common problem:

#library(ferrn)
## basic example code
